---
title: Turkey & Sage Tetrazzini with Sweet Peas, Mushrooms, and Parmesan Cream Sauce
description: First served in 1908, tetrazzini is most known for its decadent cream sauce, but our version doesn’t leave you overstuffed thanks to a little cream cheese, rather than heavy cream. Paired with a little fresh pasta, our nod to Thanksgiving couldn’t be more delicious!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/turkey-sage-tetrazzini-69c8c870.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/turkey-sage-tetrazzini-f5ed9d21.pdf
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipes/turkey-and-sage-tetrazzini-57d2d4f4f31cf1222e8b4568
author: HelloFresh
time required: 30 minutes
nutrition:
